commit 67b494e9efe449501a4733f63ebe0ce673b1f065
Author: Ade <adesulistioputra@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 31 07:50:46 2026 +0700

    Initial commit: CardVault MVP - Trading Card Marketplace with Escrow
    
    - Mobile-first PWA with Next.js 16, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
    - 15 screens: Home, Marketplace, Card Collection, Checkout, Transactions, Messages, Profile, Admin, Auth
    - Payment Gateway Abstraction Layer (Midtrans, Xendit, Stripe, PayPal)
    - IDR-first with live USD conversion
    - Escrow transaction flow with state machine
    - Prisma schema with 15 models (SQLite for dev)
    - 6 API routes for cards, listings, transactions, exchange rates, webhooks
    - Admin dashboard with gateway health monitoring

